> (PS. I looked for related issues but didn't find anything. But 3.11 has been out for a while... Am I really the first person to run into this issue?)

@newt0311 You are not the first person to experience this, I can confirm the same issue in Python 3.11, 3.12 or 3.13 (can't recall, a lot of tinkering). 

There has been a discussion about this issue and possible solutions starting with [this comment](https://github.com/cython/cython/pull/5186#issuecomment-1827578710). (It is a PR thread, so issues search does not show it). I personally opted for re-building GDB and Cython with Python 3.10 to avoid issues like this.
